    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static int UR_FLAG_ALLOW_CACHED_CREDENTIALS
      If set user name, password, and cookies may be sent with the request, and cookies may be saved from the response.(如果设置此值，用户名、密码和cookie，则可能会随请求一起发送，并且cookie可能会从响应中保存。)
      static int UR_FLAG_NO_DOWNLOAD_DATA
      If set the CefURLRequestClient.onDownloadData method will not be called.(如果设置此值，CefURLRequestClient.onDownloadData方法将不会被调用。)
      static int UR_FLAG_NO_RETRY_ON_5XX
      If set 5XX redirect errors will be propagated to the observer instead of automatically re-tried.(如果设置此值，5XX重定向错误将传递给观测者，而不是自动重试。)
      static int UR_FLAG_NONE
      Default behavior.(默认行为。)
      static int UR_FLAG_REPORT_RAW_HEADERS
      If set the headers sent and received for the request will be recorded.(如果设置此值，请求发送和接收的消息头将会被记录。)
      static int UR_FLAG_REPORT_UPLOAD_PROGRESS
      If set upload progress events will be generated when a request has a body.(如果设置此值，上传进度事件将在请求具有主体时生成。)
      static int UR_FLAG_SKIP_CACHE
      If set the cache will be skipped when handling the request.(如果设置此值，则在处理请求时将跳过缓存。)

      • UR_FLAG_NO_RETRY_ON_5XX

        public static final int UR_FLAG_NO_RETRY_ON_5XX
        If set 5XX redirect errors will be propagated to the observer instead of automatically re-tried. This currently only applies for requests originated in the browser process.(如果设置此值，5XX重定向错误将传递给观测者，而不是自动重试。目前仅适用于在浏览器进程中发出的请求。)
